creator: Glue Up
descriptionHtml:
OneTAC SG App aims to facilitate the community of Trade Associations and Chambers (TACs) in Singapore to learn, share, and connect with one another. Outreach, discussions and effective networking among the TACs are made easier with this all-in-one app. Receive announcements to keep up-to-date with what is happening in the TAC community in Singapore. Stay apprised of new policies, initiatives and events from Singapore government agencies, TACs and other business stakeholders.
This mobile app for TACs hopes to bring TACs in Singapore together as ONE Community, providing opportunities to partner and co-create initiatives.
Key features include:
·Preview upcoming events and access information including programmes, speaker bios etc.
·Easily register for events
·Direct messaging via event rooms and chats
·Themed groups for deep discussion
·Resource hub for knowledge sharing
·Digital business cards for seamless networking.
